Style "FvwmTaskBar" NoTitle, Sticky, WindowListSkip, TitleAtBottom, \
	CirculateSkip, NoHandles

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar*

*FvwmTaskBarGeometry +0-0

*FvwmTaskBarColorset 17
*FvwmTaskBarFocusColorset 18
*FvwmTaskBarIconColorset 19
*FvwmTaskBarTipsColorset 16

*FvwmTaskBarNoBrightFocus

*FvwmTaskBarFont -b&h-lucida-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmTaskBarSelFont -b&h-lucida-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

*FvwmTaskBarAction Click1 FuncFvwmDeiconifyFocusAndRaise
*FvwmTaskBarAction Click2 Iconify
*FvwmTaskBarAction Click3 Popup MenuFvwmWindowOps2 Mouse c -102m

*FvwmTaskBarUseSkipList
*FvwmTaskBarUseIconNames

*FvwmTaskBarShowTips

*FvwmTaskBarStartName 
*FvwmTaskBarStartMenu MenuFvwmRoot Mouse c -100m
*FvwmTaskBarStartIcon 16x16/penguin.xpm

*FvwmTaskBarMailCommand FuncFvwmMail
*FvwmTaskBarMailCheck 30
*FvwmTaskBarBellVolume 20

*FvwmTaskBarNoIconAction SendToModule FvwmAnimate animate
